---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DietGeneratorComponent from "../components/DietGenerator";

const title = "Free Diet Plan Generator | Personalized Meal Plans";
const description = "Generate a free, personalized diet plan based on your goals, diet type, and calorie needs. Supports Keto, Vegan, Vegetarian, and more.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <DietGeneratorComponent client:load />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-12 text-gray-700">
    <article class="prose prose-slate lg:prose-lg mx-auto">
      <h2>Why Use a Diet Plan Generator?</h2>
      <p>
        Nutrition is not one-size-fits-all. A <strong>Diet Plan Generator</strong> helps you create a structured eating schedule tailored to your specific caloric needs, dietary preferences, and health goals. Whether you want to lose weight, build muscle, or simply eat healthier, having a plan reduces decision fatigue and keeps you on track.
      </p>

      <h2>Understanding Diet Types</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8 not-prose">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">Balanced</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">A mix of carbohydrates, proteins, and fats. Ideal for general health and maintenance without strict restrictions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">Keto (Ketogenic)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">High-fat, low-carb diet that forces the body into ketosis, burning fat for fuel instead of carbohydrates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">Vegan & Vegetarian</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Plant-based diets that exclude meat (Vegetarian) or all animal products (Vegan), focusing on fruits, vegetables, and legumes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">High Protein</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Focuses on protein intake to support muscle repair and growth. Excellent for athletes and weightlifters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Key Components of a Healthy Diet</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Macronutrients:</strong> The balance of Proteins (repair), Carbohydrates (energy), and Fats (hormonal health).</li>
        <li><strong>Micronutrients:</strong> Vitamins and minerals essential for immune function and overall well-being.</li>
        <li><strong>Hydration:</strong> Drinking enough water is crucial for digestion and nutrient absorption.</li>
        <li><strong>Portion Control:</strong> Even healthy foods can lead to weight gain if consumed in excess.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tips for Sticking to Your Plan</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Meal Prep:</strong> Prepare meals in advance to avoid impulsive unhealthy choices.</li>
        <li><strong>Track Progress:</strong> Monitor how you feel and adjust calories if you're losing weight too fast or too slow.</li>
        <li><strong>Allow Flexibility:</strong> One "bad" meal won't ruin your progress. Consistency over time is what matters.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
      <div class="not-prose space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white border rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>How many calories should I eat?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            This depends on your TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure). Use our <a href="/calorie-calculator" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Calorie Calculator</a> to find your maintenance number, then subtract 300-500 for weight loss.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white border rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Is the Keto diet safe long-term?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Keto can be effective for short-term weight loss, but some find it hard to sustain. Consult a doctor before starting any restrictive diet long-term.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white border rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Can I build muscle on a Vegan diet?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Absolutely. Many plant-based sources like lentils, tofu, quinoa, and chickpeas are rich in protein. You may need to eat a higher volume of food to hit calorie targets.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
